author: Amy Greenbank
title: 'Pretty generous': Workers could double their income under JobKeeper plan
description: Eilidh Main typically works two shifts a week at a Redfern cafe. The Sydney student said a $750-a-week payment from the Federal Government's JobKeeper wage subsidy plan would double her take-home pay.
